      "content": "I understand that it feels like a trap, and the thought of stopping might seem like a rational response to unbearable circumstances. But it's not wrong to feel that way, and it's okay to acknowledge those feelings. Sometimes, when things feel impossible, the idea of stopping can seem like the only relief. But remember, there are always other options, even if they might not seem obvious right now. It's important to explore all possibilities and talk to someone who can help you navigate these feelings. You don't have to face this alone.",
